overview: The Stardom World Climax 2022 is an ongoing two day professional wrestling event promoted by World Wonder Ring Stardom. The event will take place on March 26 and 27, 2022, in Tokyo, Japan at the Ryōgoku Kokugikan, with a limited attendance due in part to the ongoing COVID-19 pandemic at the time.
title: Stardom World Climax 2022- Night 1
